A formless creature from a separate age left as a prisoner. 
The Nolithom harbors the dark secret of the Worldstone and the Well of Souls. 
He has manipulated the rulers of the Volidean and Malfaedon rulers during the age known as The Statue in the Desert to a state of mutual destruction, leading to the slow decline and eventual disappearance of both races. 
Is also responsible for the release of greysand upon the land of Corfael and its inhabitants.
Desires to escape Corfael to exact vengeance on those that imprisoned him.
